data.metadata: {"description":"Silly Billy is a great example of the kind of member every community needs. He leads by example with a naturally positive and charismatic presence that makes his content both relatable and approachable. I’ve truly enjoyed connecting with him through Abstract and our shared love for Pudgy Penguins. I’m hopeful we’ll continue to grow our connection and maybe even collaborate on some educational content to support new users. I’m looking forward to the day we get to meet at an event in person."}

translation.translatedDescription: Silly Billy is a great example of the kind of member every community needs. He leads by example with a naturally positive and charismatic presence that makes his content both relatable and approachable. I’ve truly enjoyed connecting with him through Abstract and our shared love for Pudgy Penguins. I’m hopeful we’ll continue to grow our connection and maybe even collaborate on some educational content to support new users. I’m looking forward to the day we get to meet at an event in person.

data.metadata:
{"description":"Honestly, one of the most talented artists I’ve come across in Web3

I’m not even exaggerating when I say his work leaves me speechless. It’s wild how someone this skilled can still fly under the radar—feels like the world’s missing out.

What you’re doing is incredible, man. Keep pushing, because the right people will notice. You deserve all the recognition coming your way.

Big love to you, seriously. Keep shining"}

translation.translatedDescription:
Honestly, one of the most talented artists I’ve come across in Web3

I’m not even exaggerating when I say his work leaves me speechless. It’s wild how someone this skilled can still fly under the radar—feels like the world’s missing out.

What you’re doing is incredible, man. Keep pushing, because the right people will notice. You deserve all the recognition coming your way.

Big love to you, seriously. Keep shining

Another important point is that he volunteers to be part of Operation Giga to ensure that every Thai person is taken care of, as some may experience difficulties due to the language barrier.

data.metadata: {"description":"Pavil is one of the true OGs of the Pudgy community. His passion shines through the incredible art he continues to create, especially his iconic wall pieces that have become a staple of Pudgy culture. He doesn’t just make art—he builds connection, turning every mural and sketch into a reminder of the joy and creativity at the heart of our community.\n\nWhat makes Pavil stand out isn’t only his talent but also his consistency and generosity. He keeps showing up, sharing, and inspiring others with his vision. His work captures the spirit of Pudgy Penguins in a way that feels authentic, playful, and timeless."}

translation.translatedDescription:
Pavil is one of the true OGs of the Pudgy community. His passion shines through the incredible art he continues to create, especially his iconic wall pieces that have become a staple of Pudgy culture. He doesn’t just make art—he builds connection, turning every mural and sketch into a reminder of the joy and creativity at the heart of our community.

What makes Pavil stand out isn’t only his talent but also his consistency and generosity. He keeps showing up, sharing, and inspiring others with his vision. His work captures the spirit of Pudgy Penguins in a way that feels authentic, playful, and timeless.
